# Force Unix line endings for shell scripts (prevents Windows CRLF breaking heredocs)
*.sh text eol=lf

# Cross-repo invariant: shared/fsrs.js is byte-identical (LF) across the three
# medical-PWA siblings (Geriatrics, InternalMedicine, FamilyMedicine). Without
# this rule, Windows checkouts produce CRLF in the working tree and the
# cross-repo md5 invariant check sees false-positive drift.
shared/fsrs.js text eol=lf
